**TECHNICAL IMPLEMENTATION:**

```javascript
// Before: Limited to Bankr-integrated protocols
await bankr.swap(token, amount);

// NOW: Any transaction
await bankr.submitTransaction({
  to: '0xAnyContract',
  data: encodedCalldata,
  value: ethAmount
});

// Even deploy contracts
await bankr.deployContract(bytecode, constructorArgs);
```

